    <item>
      <title>民意调查显示莫迪以压倒性优势获胜，印度股市和债券有望上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-02/india-stocks-bonds-set-to-gain-as-polls-show-landslide-modi-win</link>
      <description><![CDATA[出口民意调查显示，总理纳伦德拉·莫迪领导的政党在周六结束的大选中取得压倒性胜利，印度股市、债券和卢比有望在周一上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-02/india-stocks-bonds-set-to-gain-as-polls-show-landslide-modi-win</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 02 Jun 2024 05:10:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>沙特阿美启动巨额股票出售，以测试投资者兴趣</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-02/aramco-kicks-off-giant-share-sale-in-test-of-investor-appetite</link>
      <description><![CDATA[沙特阿美公司周日开始出售股票，为沙特阿拉伯筹集约 120 亿美元，这是近年来最大的交易之一，将考验投资者对沙特阿拉伯资产的兴趣。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-02/aramco-kicks-off-giant-share-sale-in-test-of-investor-appetite</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 02 Jun 2024 04:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>韩国金融监督院警告新税法将导致本地股票资金外流</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-02/south-korea-s-fss-warns-of-outflows-from-local-stocks-on-new-tax</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国最高金融监管机构警告称，如果明年按计划引入资本利得税，散户投资者可能会逃离本土股市。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-02/south-korea-s-fss-warns-of-outflows-from-local-stocks-on-new-tax</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 02 Jun 2024 03:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
